Why: 
1.Query as you want.
2.data can be gathered in single visit.

Q: get all books from author from title of book
[REST]
get/books/:id => title,genere,review, authorId
get/authors/:id => name, age, bio, booksID
[GraphQL]
{
    book(id:1){
        title
        gener
        review
        author{
            name
            bio
        books{
            name
        }
        }
    }
}